  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/7dccd95ba81fdfaffe08d9c755ea0e07.avif?t=1773669128\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras_big/7dccd95ba81fdfaffe08d9c755ea0e07.webp?t=1773669128 width=1560 height=343 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Days were peaceful in <strong>Majorca’s School of Witchcraft</strong>. Witches learning chromagic, cleaning their cauldron, doing rituals… you know, the usual stuff. But sometimes a witch just wants to expand their wardrobe with something colorful, stylish and, why not, for free! <br><br><strong>Abra and Cadabra</strong>, also known as the <strong>Magic Twins</strong>, have broken the 1st rule of Mallorca’s School of Witchcraft: <i>“You shall not use your chromagic powers to dye your clothes”</i> and… what the hue? Now the <strong>Colormageddon</strong> is upon us!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/5f14963a43636e3cdbe2e57de2f9ced0.poster.avif?t=1773669128\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/5f14963a43636e3cdbe2e57de2f9ced0.webm?t=1773669128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/5f14963a43636e3cdbe2e57de2f9ced0.mp4?t=1773669128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the twins in this <strong>spooky, kawaii and crazy fun local co-operative arcade tower defense game</strong> and defeat hordes of color elementals as you learn more about the Colormageddon and chromagic rituals!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/7abd2b7bf8be7727a26224f2178333a6.avif?t=1773669128\" width=615 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spells are not enough! <strong>Communication</strong> (and probably some yelling) will be invaluable to overcome all the challenges ahead of you: different objectives per level, bosses, multiple game modes, special events…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/7df465cb1b762f134d1d423abd7dd832.poster.avif?t=1773669128\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/7df465cb1b762f134d1d423abd7dd832.webm?t=1773669128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/7df465cb1b762f134d1d423abd7dd832.mp4?t=1773669128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/ccf2ff1d1ce3f877731a6d23af957fd7.avif?t=1773669128\" width=615 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features 2D art with spooky kawaii vibes. Do you want cute skins? We have them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/b1399b0675e4369ad8d307987478c4aa.poster.avif?t=1773669128\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/b1399b0675e4369ad8d307987478c4aa.webm?t=1773669128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/b1399b0675e4369ad8d307987478c4aa.mp4?t=1773669128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/0cf25ca3cfc3274b0ab51a774ba8bf0e.avif?t=1773669128\" width=615 height=84 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A COOPERATIVE GAME WHERE QUICK REFLEXES WILL SAVE THE DAY!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Aim and fire</strong> your chromagic: Red beats red, blue beats blue… easy right?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple enemies with unique mechanics. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot your spells and <strong>defeat the hordes before they reach your barrier.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fill your cauldron with magic, coordinate with your partner and cast a <strong>special charm</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Change between the twins in <strong>1 player mode</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Coordinate</strong> your powers in 2 <strong>player co-op mode</strong> to overcome all rituals!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPLORE THE B-HUE-TIFUL MALLORCA’S SCHOOL OF WITCHCRAFT!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>7 areas to visit</strong> and make rituals in.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Up to 39 levels</strong> with their own requirements. Get 3 stars for each level!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the <strong>secrets</strong> and secondary objectives to master Chromagic.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get all the <strong>achievements</strong> and show off!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A MAGICAL EXPERIENCE FULL OF SPOOKY YET KAWAII FUN!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your wardrobe with lots of <strong>themed skins! Witches with style!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Accessible</strong> for everyone. Change the <strong>color filter</strong> for: Protanopia, protanomaly, deuteranopia, deuteranomaly, tritanopia, tritanomaly, achromatopsia and achromatomaly.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Colorful</strong> cartoon <strong>2D art, kawaii</strong> sounds, <strong>magical</strong> music, lovely characters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast paced and crazy fun combat mechanic. Magical Twins await!</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/7dccd95ba81fdfaffe08d9c755ea0e07.avif?t=1773669128\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras_big/7dccd95ba81fdfaffe08d9c755ea0e07.webp?t=1773669128 width=1560 height=343 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Days were peaceful in <strong>Majorca’s School of Witchcraft</strong>. Witches learning chromagic, cleaning their cauldron, doing rituals… you know, the usual stuff. But sometimes a witch just wants to expand their wardrobe with something colorful, stylish and, why not, for free! <br><br><strong>Abra and Cadabra</strong>, also known as the <strong>Magic Twins</strong>, have broken the 1st rule of Mallorca’s School of Witchcraft: <i>“You shall not use your chromagic powers to dye your clothes”</i> and… what the hue? Now the <strong>Colormageddon</strong> is upon us!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/5f14963a43636e3cdbe2e57de2f9ced0.poster.avif?t=1773669128\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/5f14963a43636e3cdbe2e57de2f9ced0.webm?t=1773669128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/5f14963a43636e3cdbe2e57de2f9ced0.mp4?t=1773669128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the twins in this <strong>spooky, kawaii and crazy fun local co-operative arcade tower defense game</strong> and defeat hordes of color elementals as you learn more about the Colormageddon and chromagic rituals!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/7abd2b7bf8be7727a26224f2178333a6.avif?t=1773669128\" width=615 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spells are not enough! <strong>Communication</strong> (and probably some yelling) will be invaluable to overcome all the challenges ahead of you: different objectives per level, bosses, multiple game modes, special events…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/7df465cb1b762f134d1d423abd7dd832.poster.avif?t=1773669128\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/7df465cb1b762f134d1d423abd7dd832.webm?t=1773669128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/7df465cb1b762f134d1d423abd7dd832.mp4?t=1773669128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/ccf2ff1d1ce3f877731a6d23af957fd7.avif?t=1773669128\" width=615 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features 2D art with spooky kawaii vibes. Do you want cute skins? We have them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/b1399b0675e4369ad8d307987478c4aa.poster.avif?t=1773669128\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/b1399b0675e4369ad8d307987478c4aa.webm?t=1773669128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/b1399b0675e4369ad8d307987478c4aa.mp4?t=1773669128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1270080/extras/0cf25ca3cfc3274b0ab51a774ba8bf0e.avif?t=1773669128\" width=615 height=84 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A COOPERATIVE GAME WHERE QUICK REFLEXES WILL SAVE THE DAY!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Aim and fire</strong> your chromagic: Red beats red, blue beats blue… easy right?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple enemies with unique mechanics. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot your spells and <strong>defeat the hordes before they reach your barrier.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fill your cauldron with magic, coordinate with your partner and cast a <strong>special charm</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Change between the twins in <strong>1 player mode</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Coordinate</strong> your powers in 2 <strong>player co-op mode</strong> to overcome all rituals!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPLORE THE B-HUE-TIFUL MALLORCA’S SCHOOL OF WITCHCRAFT!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>7 areas to visit</strong> and make rituals in.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Up to 39 levels</strong> with their own requirements. Get 3 stars for each level!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the <strong>secrets</strong> and secondary objectives to master Chromagic.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get all the <strong>achievements</strong> and show off!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A MAGICAL EXPERIENCE FULL OF SPOOKY YET KAWAII FUN!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your wardrobe with lots of <strong>themed skins! Witches with style!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Accessible</strong> for everyone. Change the <strong>color filter</strong> for: Protanopia, protanomaly, deuteranopia, deuteranomaly, tritanopia, tritanomaly, achromatopsia and achromatomaly.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Colorful</strong> cartoon <strong>2D art, kawaii</strong> sounds, <strong>magical</strong> music, lovely characters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast paced and crazy fun combat mechanic. Magical Twins await!</p></li></ul>",
